STUNNING HOSTESSES, COCTAIL WAITRESSES NEEDED – TOP NIGHTCLUB - ABU DHABI!
High profile Hospitality Group with stunning a stunning venue in Abu Dhabi, are looking to recruit “the best of the best” – they are looking for awesome HOSTESSES to strengthen their current teams!
We need candidates who are well spoken and well presented – driven, dynamic with a positive attitude and a real desire to succeed! My client is looking for individuals who have strong and solid work experience in High Profile Nightclubs, Bars, Top Restaurants or Prestigious hotels!
Candidates must have a good work ethic, positive attitude and a real passion for what they do!
Salaries: Good basic salaries offered with full expat benefits including shared accommodation (dependent upon role), service charge, medical, flights and the chance to develop your career in an expanding and very exciting company!
TO APPLY PLEASE SEND YOUR UPDATED CV + PROFILE PICTURE
